-Open Terminal

-Clone repository using command $ git clone .....

-Bundle install gem files

-Run $ postgres and the in another tab run $ psql

-The past the following code in your psql command line:

  =# CREATE DATABASE hair_salon;
  =# \c hair_salon;
  =# CREATE TABLE clients(id serial PRIMARY KEY, name varchar, contact_number varchar, gender varchar);
  CREATE TABLE
  =# CREATE TABLE stylists(id serial PRIMARY KEY, name varchar, client_id int);

-Then in your bash command line $ ruby app.rb and open a browser localhost:4567/
